win11-window-tiling — Arch Linux KDE Plasma Edition
===================================================

Windows 11-style window tiling for Arch Linux with KDE Plasma and KZones.

Install (after building the package)
------------------------------------

  sudo pacman -U win11-window-tiling-kde-1.0.0-1-any.pkg.tar.zst

Setup
-----

  win11-tiling-setup

Log out and back in, then verify KZones in KWin Scripts.

License: KZones GPL-3.0; scripts MIT.